When menu type is `menu`, name property is read from the vue file. 
This is designed for `keep-alive` pages, so you won't worry about spell the name wrong which could cause `keep-alive` not working. 
If you want to change it, please change it in the vue file and refresh the page, the you will get the new name.

当菜单类型是menu时，name是从对应的vue文件读取的，即vue的name属性。
此处设计是为了避免name拼写错误而导致的keep-alive失效问题。
如果想要修改name，请到对应的vue文件中修改name属性，最后刷新页面，即可获得修改后的name。

Generated by vite `globEager` feature. 
For default setup, it will scan all vue files under `src` 
Set `defaultView` false (same level with setup) in the vue file to make current vue file not showing in the select options.

默认扫描src下的所有vue文件。
设置`defaultView`为false（与name/setup同级的属性）即可让当前vue文件不显示在下拉框的数组之中。

Indicates that user has notified the system that they prefer an interface that removes or replaces the types of motion-based animation that trigger discomfort for those with vestibular motion disorders.

`global` means all pages using the same animation
`scope` means using `router.meta.animationMode` field

`global`意味着所有页面通用一个切换动画
`scope`意味着采用路由的meta中的指定动画字段

`Always` means show all the time.
`Overflow` means only show when tab is overflowed.

`Always` 意味着始终展示。
`Overflow` 意味着只在选项卡溢出时展示。

'normal' means no change to route query
'enhanced' means make query unreadable

'normal' 即正常路由query
'enhanced' 即对query进行处理，让用户无法直观的观察到query里的内容

'base64' 即序列化后进行base64的转换
'cryptojs' 即对query进行一定城的加密/解密

'base64' means will stringify the query and transform to base64
'cryptojs' means will use key/iv to encrypt/decrypt the query

'scope' means use `watermark` content in route meta
'global' means the whole application will add watermark

'scope' 意味着会采用路由的meta中的watermark相关配置，可独立为每一页配置不同的水印
'global' 意味着全局采用相同的watermark配置
Set this true, the app will use event listener to hijack the `F5` event with redirect the route. (Lots of the app state will stay the same)
开启时，系统会监听 F5 事件并拦截，使用路由的重定向模式实现刷新的效果（当然只是局部刷新，页面的很多状态都还在）。
